{"tid":1541992,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[落伍JJ] HTC u12 plus定iphone 7","createTime":"2019-09-04T17:17:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T08:15:55.000Z","uid":282284,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"cd21be596acd96f1a9a3e5d1360c2cc79c6c6384","tid":1541992,"uid":282284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:17:57.000Z","msg":"我知應該有人覺得我依家先買呢2款好outdated<br />\n但我一向唔係追款 <br />\n亦唔想花好多錢買一部死物<br />\n希望各位畀下意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n原本用開iphone SE<br />\n用咗3年左右<br />\n整過2次, 早排正式壽終正寢<br />\n<br />\n鐘意mon唔太大<br />\n電話首要條件希望影相唔錯<br />\n都唔好太易壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n曾經我發過誓唔再用iphone<br />\n因為真係好快壞<br />\n但我本身link晒ipad 而且用慣咗<br />\n見依家7跌到$5000內<br />\n可接受<br />\n<br />\n考慮HTC係因為以前用過desire<br />\n印象唔錯 <br />\n雖然依家HTC手機好似好頹<br />\n但我真係畀u12 plus相機吸引到<br />\n<br />\n利申 唔需要叫我考慮samsung, 唔知點解好憎呢個brand, 應該唔會考慮了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5c9ab0db7323fde2d76dccf4e14fa265c0c3069","tid":1541992,"uid":117906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:18:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"96c548972a60c3a405351cd142b60e03f0aa9e7a","tid":1541992,"uid":119607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:20:04.000Z","msg":"iPhone 啦"},{"pid":"921b39fc01d4cfe603ee474260eb51bc2d44dd57","tid":1541992,"uid":45957,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:21:15.000Z","msg":"等到出11再買8"},{"pid":"7bc9e1d5674d45e1c33966e152098326d921169b","tid":1541992,"uid":776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:21:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"14316f90515315b06ad31bf75b5e41d7f3139104","tid":1541992,"uid":279952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:23:15.000Z","msg":"緊係iphone 喇"},{"pid":"2a10344777760a03dde0cc1dbee27a2c7d358caf","tid":1541992,"uid":128489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:31:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4630a4586d534a339806c79643db81379ade7fbc","tid":1541992,"uid":282284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"921b39fc01d4cfe603ee474260eb51bc2d44dd57","tid":1541992,"uid":45957,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:21:15.000Z","msg":"等到出11再買8"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:38:42.000Z","msg":"256gb會跌到$5000內?<br />\n64gb唔係好夠用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:"},{"pid":"99a7b3608ff0382a3b9476c1df1200c494a81cf7","tid":1541992,"uid":282284,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7bc9e1d5674d45e1c33966e152098326d921169b","tid":1541992,"uid":776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:21:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:39:50.000Z","msg":"可能我成日跌電話 感覺上比之前其他機脆弱好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91155282193fa70a4055bab299c30f7803917e3c","tid":1541992,"uid":134437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T00:20:46.000Z","msg":"iPhone x